{
  "stem": "6803.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was before the liberation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Before that-- I understood at that time that that was the, uh-- the end of it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we heard-- we heard-- yes, we heard a lot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they gave us a hot soup, really hot soup.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they gave us five minutes to finish it, and we couldn't eat it because it was too hot.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And while we were standing and as soon as we start marching, we were not allowed to have the soup.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Throw it away.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we marched from Mauthausen to Gunskirchen for about five or six days.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Didn't give us a piece of bread, not a glass of water, nothing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were just walking like animals.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And what we ate-- and we weren't allowed to do that either, but I was watching the SS, should not catch me.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We ate the, uh-- the, uh-- whatchamacallit-- the bugs from the grass, on the grass.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We ate that in order to stay alive, and I couldn't eat it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "People were eating, and they says, eat it!",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You gotta eat it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So-- so anyway, so, uh-- so we were marching.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And one time they were-- there was-- there was, uh-- I don't know the name of that little town.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We were passing by--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Gusen Zwei.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On a march to Gunskirchen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To destroy us, to kill us all.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On a march.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took us on a march, and we marched through a little town-- I don't know the name.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If I would have knowed the name of that town and I would know, remember where it was, I would have gone back after the war.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The reason why, we were marching by, and there was people sitting in the balcony.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
